title: Governor's Award for Agricultural Achievement presented to Missouri producers Pa… (State of Missouri)
text: ( Source : State of Missouri ) Dairy farmer Paul Heins , of Higginsville, and pork producer Brent Sandidge, of Marshall , were each recognized today with a Governor's Award for Agricultural Achievement, which honors outstanding farmers, growers
